# EventType: 12165106
#
# Descriptor: [B+ -> (D~0 -> (KS0 -> pi+ pi-) pi+ pi-) K+]cc
#
# NickName: Bu_D0K,KSpipi=gamma,DecProdCut
#
# Cuts: DaughtersInLHCb
#
# Documentation: Charged B to D K, where D could be D0 or anti-D0. Interference of
#                   D0/anti-D0 is taken into account by means of gamma, delta and rB.
#                   D decays to Ks pi+ pi-. Decay products in acceptance.
#
# PhysicsWG:   B2OC
# Tested:      Yes
# Responsible: Jordi Garra Ticó
# Email:       jordi.garra.tico@cern.ch
# Date:        20120220

Alias      my-D0        D0
Alias      my-anti-D0   anti-D0
Alias      my-KS        K_S0

ChargeConj my-D0        my-anti-D0
ChargeConj my-KS        my-KS

# CPV parameters.
Define gamma 1.22 # 70º
Define delta 2.27 # 130º
Define rB    0.10



Decay B+sig
1.000     my-anti-D0 K+        BTODDALITZCPK gamma delta rB;
Enddecay
CDecay B-sig

Decay my-D0
1.000     my-KS pi+ pi-        D0GAMMADALITZ;
Enddecay
CDecay my-anti-D0

Decay my-KS
1.000     pi+  pi-             PHSP;
Enddecay

End
